#

Herb-Crusted New York Strip Steak with Truffle Mashed Potatoes

$45
800 kcal

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

SteakComfort FoodGourmet

Description

A succulent New York strip steak encrusted with herbs, served alongside creamy truffle-infused mashed potatoes for an indulgent experience.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 2 large pieces
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic Cloves: 4, minced
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Heavy Cream: 1 cup
  • Truffle Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Potatoes: 2 pounds, peeled and cubed
